[14/10/2018 12:15:50] <font color="#ffff00">¡Y Fabiola Saglimbeni!</font>
[14/10/2018 12:15:54] <font color="#ffff00">Os presento; jurado, participantes;</font>
[14/10/2018 12:15:54] <font color="#ffff00">participantes, jurado.</font>
